description: MakingORG, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, purchases and sells Acer truncatum bunge seed oil in the People's Republic of China. It offers Acer truncatum bunge seed oil to third parties to manufacture Acer truncatum bunge related health products. The company was formerly known as Drimex Inc. and changed its name to MakingORG, Inc. in August 2014. MakingORG, Inc. was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Walnut, California.
